I have 2.3 Gigs of photos of KSP projects I've worked on over the last year or so.  There are 1,639 photos in total I have screenshotted.  Here is a small sample of my life's work in our favorite simulation game.  Feel free to share your crafts through photos here as well! 

Let me know which ones were your favorites!! (Obviously I'm really proud of the Moth SSTO and Dallas Station.)

Facebook post with photos here.
2.3? phhh, I have almost exactly 3 GB!
